  <brief_title>Evaluation of Tolerability and Safety of &quot;Allergovac Poliplus&quot; in Polysensitized Patients With Rhinitis or Allergic Rhinoconjunctivitis With or Without Asthma: A Study in Daily Clinical Practice</brief_title>
  <acronym>APOLO</acronym>
  <official_title>Evaluation of Tolerability and Safety of &quot;Allergovac Poliplus&quot; in Polysensitized Patients With Rhinitis or Allergic Rhinoconjunctivitis With or Without Asthma: A Study in Daily Clinical Practice</official_title>
  <sponsors>
